ZH: 我想用现款付款。
EN: I want to pay in cash.

ZH: 这家商店只接受现款。
EN: This shop only accepts cash.

ZH: 他拿了现款到银行存款。
EN: He took the cash to the bank for deposit.

ZH: 我们需要现款才能买车。
EN: We need cash to buy a car.

ZH: 你可以用现款买这个包。
EN: You can buy this bag with cash.

ZH: 我用现款支付了账单。
EN: I paid the bill with cash.

ZH: 我不喜欢刷卡，我更喜欢用现款。
EN: I don't like using cards, I prefer cash.

ZH: 现款支付的话可以享受10%的折扣。
EN: You can get a 10% discount if you pay in cash.

ZH: 他们只接受人民币现款。
EN: They only accept cash in Chinese yuan.

ZH: 这家商店没有刷卡机，只接受现款。
EN: This shop doesn't have a card machine, only cash is accepted.

ZH: 我们只接受现款，不接受支票。
EN: We only accept cash, no checks.

ZH: 刷卡是一种方便的支付方式，但现款更安全。
EN: Paying with cards is a convenient payment method, but cash is safer.

ZH: 这家餐厅只接受现款，不接受信用卡。
EN: This restaurant only accepts cash, no credit cards.

ZH: 请准备好现款，以便快速结账。
EN: Please have the cash ready for a quick checkout.

ZH: 我们不接受外币，只接受人民币现款。
EN: We don't accept foreign currencies, only cash in Chinese yuan.

ZH: 现款支付的话可以避免支付额外的手续费。
EN: Paying in cash can avoid additional transaction fees.

ZH: 他们只接受交易额在500元以上的现款。
EN: They only accept cash transactions of 500 yuan or more.

ZH: 他喜欢用现款购买高价值的商品。
EN: He prefers buying high-value items with cash.

ZH: 这家商店提供现款优惠，无需额外付费。
EN: This shop offers a cash discount, with no extra charge.

ZH: 现款支付速度更快，不会浪费时间。
EN: Paying in cash is faster and won't waste time.
